OL,3,CParalympian Tanni Grey-Thompson had to
OL,4,C'crawl off train' at London King's
OL,5,CCross
OL,7,FOne of Britain's most decorated
OL,8,FParalympians had to "crawl off a
OL,9,Ftrain" at London King's Cross station
OL,10,Fbecause no-one was there to help her,
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,FBaroness Tanni Grey-Thompson travelled
OL,14,Fon a train from Leeds to London King's
OL,15,FCross on Monday evening but arrived at
OL,16,F10pm to find no-one there to help and
OL,17,Fsaid she was left waiting for 16
OL,18,Fminutes.
