OL,3,CParalympian Tanni Grey-Thompson had to
OL,4,C'crawl off train' at London King's
OL,5,CCross
OL,7,FBaroness Grey-Thompson, who has spina
OL,8,Fbifida, was a wheelchair racer and
OL,9,Fcompeted in five Games between 1988
OL,10,Fand 2004.
OL,12,FShe claimed 11 gold medals, plus four
OL,13,Fsilvers and a bronze, and was created
OL,14,Fa life peer in 2010.
OL,16,FShe told BBC Radio 4's Today programme
OL,17,Fthat she missed her 7.15pm train and
OL,18,Fgot on the 7.45pm service, but when
OL,19,Fshe arrived at King's Cross no-one was
OL,20,Fthere to meet her.
