OL,7,FSo I'm going to Paris later today,
OL,8,FI've got a few bags, had to chuck them
OL,9,Fon the platform, get out of my chair,
OL,10,Fsit on the floor right by the door,
OL,11,Fwhich is not particularly pleasant,
OL,12,Fand then crawl off."
OL,14,FShe added: "There was no-one around. I
OL,15,Fmean, I was pretty angry last night."
