OL,7,F"The booking system is not
OL,8,Fparticularly fit for purpose. Every
OL,9,Ftrain company does things slightly
OL,10,Fdifferently.
OL,12,F"You know, we were meant to have level
OL,13,Fboarding in the UK January 1st 2020,
OL,14,Funder the Disability Discrimination
OL,15,FAct, every single government has
OL,16,Fkicked the can down the road.
