OL,7,FAlison Kerry, head of communications
OL,8,Fat disability equality charity Scope,
OL,9,Fsaid "this is a sad reminder that far
OL,10,Ftoo often disabled people get treated
OL,11,Flike second-class citizens.
OL,13,F"On the eve of the Paralympics it
OL,14,Fhighlights how much further we need to
OL,15,Fgo; it shouldn't be this difficult for
OL,16,Fa wheelchair user to use public
OL,17,Ftransport.
